{"data":[{"name":"104:1","price":"伤哉！每个诽谤者，诋毁者，","arabic":"وَيۡلٞ لِّكُلِّ هُمَزَةٖ لُّمَزَةٍ","category":["104 (Al-Humazah)","Al-Humazah","Surah Al-Humazah"],"ayahNumber":6180,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh","meta":{"transliteration":"waylun likulli humazatin lumazatin ","translations":["Woe","to every","slanderer","backbiter","(1)"],"transliterationArr":["waylun","likulli","humazatin","lumazatin",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,690],[2,690,1860],[3,1860,2810],[4,2810,4535]]}},{"name":"104:2","price":"他聚积财产, 而当作武器，","arabic":"ٱلَّذِي جَمَعَ مَالٗا وَعَدَّدَهُۥ","category":["104 (Al-Humazah)","Al-Humazah","Surah Al-Humazah"],"ayahNumber":6181,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh","meta":{"transliteration":"alladhī jamaʿa mālan waʿaddadahu ","translations":["The one who","collects","wealth","and counts it","(2)"],"transliterationArr":["alladhī","jamaʿa","mālan","waʿaddadahu",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1120],[2,1120,1830],[3,1830,2950],[4,2950,5305]]}},{"name":"104:3","price":"他以为他的财产，能使他不灭。","arabic":"يَحۡسَبُ أَنَّ مَالَهُۥٓ أَخۡلَدَهُۥ","category":["104 (Al-Humazah)","Al-Humazah","Surah Al-Humazah"],"ayahNumber":6182,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh","meta":{"transliteration":"yaḥsabu anna mālahu akhladahu ","translations":["Thinking","that","his wealth","will make him immortal","(3)"],"transliterationArr":["yaḥsabu","anna","mālahu","akhladahu",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,910],[2,910,2410],[3,2410,4890],[4,4890,6575]]}},{"name":"104:4","price":"绝不然，他必定要被投在毁灭坑中。","arabic":"كَلَّاۖ لَيُنۢبَذَنَّ فِي ٱلۡحُطَمَةِ","category":["104 (Al-Humazah)","Al-Humazah","Surah Al-Humazah"],"ayahNumber":6183,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh","meta":{"transliteration":"kallā layunbadhanna fī al-ḥuṭamati ","translations":["Nay","Surely he will be thrown","in","the Crusher","(4)"],"transliterationArr":["kallā","layunbadhanna","fī","al-ḥuṭamati",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,970],[2,970,4800],[3,4800,5090],[4,5090,6665]]}},{"name":"104:5","price":"你怎能知道毁灭坑是什么？","arabic"